Use the standard library
This is how to hex_key of num:
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this num's length times:
    Remember that ch is tostring of item i in num
    When ch is in "ABCDEF", then:
      Increase count by 1
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is quotient of count and 2
